+ Restricted :
  - Gambits OK
  - Sacrifices OK
  - NEVER RESIGN

+ Know :
  - Basic and advanced tactics
  - Master E4 - E5 opening theory
  - Checkmate patterns
  - New openings besides 4 Knights
  - Oposition
  - Pawn, and Rook endgames
  - Lucena
  - Philidor
  - N vs B endgames
  - key squares
  - Pawn structures

+ Foundation :
  - Don't blunder any pieces and take free pieces
  - Master previous habits!
  - Know where the Rooks belong
  - Avoid trades when down material/trade when up
